            <lg xml:id="TK341">
<l>yātaṉiṉ yātaṉi ṉīṅkiyā ṉōta</l>
<l>lataṉi ṉataṉi ṉilaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Whatever thing, a man has renounced, by that thing; he cannot suffer pain.</l>
            </lg>
